### Get All Players
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players

### Get Player by ID (replace with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/PLAYER-ID-HERE

### Get Player by Name
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/name/Ryan

